data.description: Gorgeous new McKinley Carriage plan by D.R. Horton in beautiful Preserves of Carroll Creek West. This floor plan has everything on your list and more with 4 bedrooms (all with walk-in closets), 2.5 baths and included 3 car garage. You will love the open layout of this 2 story home which features a spacious great room, main level den, convenient upstairs laundry and impressive bed and bath #1. Photos representative of plan only and may vary as built.
